      <div class="card card--lg"><div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;margin-bottom:14px;"><div style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:11px;background:rgba(26,39,68,0.09);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A2744" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2L2 22h20L12 2z"/><path d="M12 9v6M12 18v.01"/></svg></div><div class="lead-num" style="margin:0;">03</div></div><h3 class="h2 mb-2">Incident Reporting</h3><p class="text-secondary body mb-3">Capture incidents and near-misses from the floor in seconds, with photos, location, and witnesses attached automatically. Multi-level investigation workflow with root-cause analysis. From incident to closure on one digital trail.</p><a href="#" class="btn-tertiary arrow-right">Explore Incident Reporting</a></div>
