        <h3 style="font-size:22px;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:12px;">Generosity</h3>
        <div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--steel-700);font-style:italic;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:14px;">We share what works.</div>
        <p style="font-size:13.5px;color:var(--steel-700);line-height:1.55;margin:0;">Methodologies, templates, frameworks, field notes. The industry gets better when we share what we've learned, and so do we.</p>
