        <div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--steel-700);font-style:italic;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:14px;">We don't panic during incidents. That's the whole point.</div>
        <p style="font-size:13.5px;color:var(--steel-700);line-height:1.55;margin:0;">Calm, structured, deliberate response, to safety events at customer sites and to service incidents on our own platform. Composure is operational.</p>
      </div>

